text: President Trump has relished making mail-in voting a boogeyman during the coronavirus pandemic, denouncing the method routinely as part of his longstanding and evidence-free crusade over alleged voter fraud. Now he's making an exception for Florida. https://t.co/LVNIyvN1OG
